intent.user_query: What is the total revenue per product type?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductType;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID GROUP BY p.ProductType;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
